# Keep the Rust build context small. The legacy Python tree is long gone;
# what ships: the workspace, e2e suites, docs (mdBook site includes them),
# and the model_eval datasets used by mnemosyne-bench.
*
!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock
!crates
!crates/**
!tests/e2e.sh
!tests/e2e-backends.sh
!docs
!docs/**
!website
!website/**
!benchmarks/model_eval/datasets
!benchmarks/model_eval/datasets/**
!README.md
